    "description": "Foxblade is an Action-RPG Solodev game where you forge your strengths through battle, as a lone hero you complete quests, find powerful random weapons and artifacts to boost your powers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Choose between three main playstyles</strong></li></ul>Do you like to be in the frontlines where the glory lies? <u>Then Melee combat is for you.</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/c3a3c467c7f155547d8b83263719fd1e.poster.avif?t=1682044392\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/c3a3c467c7f155547d8b83263719fd1e.webm?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/c3a3c467c7f155547d8b83263719fd1e.mp4?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Do you prefer flank your enemies from the distance and strike them to the ground before they can even reach you? <u>Then Ranged combat is your choice.</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/d2718579e967abdb1206f7cc7b0a0c39.poster.avif?t=1682044392\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/d2718579e967abdb1206f7cc7b0a0c39.webm?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/d2718579e967abdb1206f7cc7b0a0c39.mp4?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Or do you prefer invoke the fury of the arcane magic, and smite, shock and burn your enemies with incredible spells? <u>Then your choice lies with Magic <br>combat.</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/5c4915f4bf45bc84618267ed75060227.poster.avif?t=1682044392\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/5c4915f4bf45bc84618267ed75060227.webm?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/5c4915f4bf45bc84618267ed75060227.mp4?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Quick and responsive action combat</strong></li></ul></h2><br>Attack quickly and master the dodge mechanic to become nearly untouchable. Help yourself with abilities you learn when leveling up.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/4121614d0cd25a7835534876f3e75086.poster.avif?t=1682044392\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/4121614d0cd25a7835534876f3e75086.webm?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/4121614d0cd25a7835534876f3e75086.mp4?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Special abilities</strong></li></ul></h2><br>Level up your weapon of choice and learn special abilities depending on the weapon you use and crush your enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/2344deb4bc0d939562489867a98e8b69.poster.avif?t=1682044392\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/2344deb4bc0d939562489867a98e8b69.webm?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/2344deb4bc0d939562489867a98e8b69.mp4?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Item Sets and  Randomized loot</strong></li></ul></h2><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each item has a specific main color, if all the items you have equipped have the same color you get a bonus depending on the weapon type you have equipped.</li></ul></strong><br><br>There are 4 types of quality in items:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Common, Uncommon, Rare and Unique.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each one superior to the previous one.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each item spawn with a slightly randomized stats making them one of a kind.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Unique weapons has special lore behind them that can be read in the item description.</u></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/2003eddb93706d7292f87149af65e78c.poster.avif?t=1682044392\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/2003eddb93706d7292f87149af65e78c.webm?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/2003eddb93706d7292f87149af65e78c.mp4?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Main and Optional Quests</strong></li></ul></h2><br>Help the inhabitants of this strange land, befriend them, get awesome rewards for a job well done and earn your place in this world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/5e29e6e9a8e8f37245d09356bb7af303.poster.avif?t=1682044392\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/5e29e6e9a8e8f37245d09356bb7af303.webm?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351100/extras/5e29e6e9a8e8f37245d09356bb7af303.mp4?t=1682044392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
